name: Luna
description:
Luna (ルナ, Runa) is a black cat who is a devoted servant to Princess Serenity and advisor to her mother, Queen Serenity. When the kingdom falls, she and Artemis are put into a long sleep and sent to Earth to look after the Sailor Guardians, who are reborn there.

3000x3000 px PNG file

This is the 4th installment of the Todxs Caretas / Original Fakes series, that consists of collectible avatars depicting myths, symbols, monsters and icons from everyday culture, high arts and pop culture. 

All of them made by hand on papercut technic.
